entry.title: Collider Dodecahedron
entry.content:
No.S01: Collider Dodecahedron

Price: US$ 240

Mechanism: Face turning pentakis dodecahedron

Axis of Rotation: 60 axes

Diameter (inner): 90 mm

Material: PETG (FDM)

First Completion Date: 2024-06-07

Collider Dodecahedron was originally designed by David Pitcher, but due to the difficulty of assembling his version, he did not sell it. Now I’ve designed my version and have Pitcher’s permission to sell this puzzle, thanks to Pitcher’s generosity!

Pictures

Note

The price is for the puzzle along with one set of stickers. I will assemble and break in the puzzle for you, and you’ll need to sticker it yourself. Contact me via Instagram or email with any needs or questions.

Contact

Instagram (recommended): KairisPuzzles

Email:kairispuzzles@outlook.com
